qas.question: Voter demographics of florida in the 1950's

answers.text: 1952 to 1964, most voters were registered Democrats, but the state voted for the Republican presidential candidate in every election except for 1964

qas.question: what did the voting rights act provide for

answers.text: Voting Rights Act of 1965, providing for oversight of state practices and enforcement of constitutional voting rights for African Americans and other minorities

qas.question: what president signed the voting right act

answers.text: President Lyndon B. Johnson signed the Voting Rights Act of 1965
